aboutParagraph.para: I am passionate about what I do and doing it well is my goal.
Some people call me adefam, but I am Famosa Adegbite Temitayo. I grew up in Osogbo, Osun State, Nigeria.
I studied Computer Science at Osun State College of Technology and further my degree program in Computer Science at Osun State University.
Trained in various computer related application and certified with many.
Skilled in Software Engineer, Frontend, Backend, Database Administrator, Data Science and Analysis, UI/UX Design, GoogleLing, Training/Mentoring, Soft-Skills and more...
